{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2340575, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 447971, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "除非是专业性很强，格式要求严格的PPT、文章，用latex都是相对不方便的，还是所见即所得的word/PPT 好用\n", "timestamp": 1629713314, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340576, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 447971, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "方便", "timestamp": 1629713330, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340583, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 447971, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可能我更习惯所想即所得的Latex，word和PPT这种我都是能不用就不用", "timestamp": 1629713370, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340587, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 447971, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "做普通PPT：更繁琐\n做数学类PPT（很多公式）：还不错，和Powerpoint不相上下\n写很多公式的论文：yyds", "timestamp": 1629713402, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340589, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 447971, "reply_to": 2340583, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 感觉大多数人还是更习惯所见即所得吧（比如我）", "timestamp": 1629713434, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340631, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 447971, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "ppt不是论文作图工具吗？（暴论", "timestamp": 1629713794, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340639, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 447971, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我感觉LaTeX的适用场景是，排版模式固定、只用填内容的文档/演示文稿，像企业里那种一页换一个版式的LaTeX就不适合，但做数学课件就很方便", "timestamp": 1629713868, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340644, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 447971, "reply_to": 2340589, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: dz专业几乎没有公式 那还是PowerPoint好用？就是想latex是不是能装逼哈哈", "timestamp": 1629713899, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340662, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 447971, "reply_to": 2340639, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 明白了，谢谢dave，这么说来应该ppt更合适", "timestamp": 1629713954, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340695, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 447971, "reply_to": 2340644, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 没有公式就完全没必要了，latex排版功能学起来有点复杂", "timestamp": 1629714272, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2340880, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 447971, "reply_to": 2340695, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 好！", "timestamp": 1629716129, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 447971, "reply": 11, "tag": null, "text": "求问latex做ppt方便吗？想学", "timestamp": 1629712731, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1629716130, "url": "", "vote": {}}}